msgid "Asking for questions."
msgstr "让学生提出疑问。"

#: introduction/xinclude.xml:1283(para)
msgid "Asking questions."
msgstr "对学生提出问题。"

#: introduction/xinclude.xml:1286(para)
msgid ""
"Using the Lesson Summary presentation slide, which highlight the main points."
msgstr ""
"使用课程总结幻灯片，并在其中标明重点。"

